Second of all, if we accept that smaller class sizes can be help-- Well,

247
00:12:11.528 --> 00:12:14.368
I'm sure you probably do remember the number of people in your class.

248
00:12:15.548 --> 00:12:16.348
Mark would.

249
00:12:16.368 --> 00:12:17.468
But that's not normal.

250
00:12:20.004 --> 00:12:21.404
And it is considered observable.

251
00:12:21.424 --> 00:12:21.544
So-

252
00:12:22.374 --> 00:12:25.884
Well, some would use other expressions-

253
00:12:26.584 --> 00:12:28.124
But I'm trying to be good for the rest of the week.

254
00:12:28.364 --> 00:12:29.474
Um, the-

255
00:12:29.744 --> 00:12:30.694
I appreciate that, Minister

256
00:12:30.904 --> 00:12:31.204
The

