265
00:13:02.064 --> 00:13:05.064
So by redirecting their funding to get smaller sizes, it's very useful.

266
00:13:05.104 --> 00:13:08.924
Another thing they can do, one charter school in the past actually had

267
00:13:09.384 --> 00:13:13.184
more classes per day, longer hours for the teachers,

268
00:13:13.684 --> 00:13:15.904
but the quid pro quo was that they got

