271
00:13:24.884 --> 00:13:28.644
shut down by an incoming labor government, and it

272
00:13:28.724 --> 00:13:32.434
lost its business model because it was forced to have union contracts,

273
00:13:32.504 --> 00:13:34.724
which did not tolerate that flexibility.

274
00:13:35.224 --> 00:13:38.704
I think that's a really interesting example for people on the political left to

275
00:13:38.744 --> 00:13:42.024
reflect on. However, there are other innovations that are possible.

276
00:13:42.444 --> 00:13:46.304
If you were to go to Mastery School in Christchurch, for example, they

