00:13:49.564 --> 00:13:53.204
apprenticeships to education students from the University of

279
00:13:53.244 --> 00:13:57.144
Canterbury. And this is a win-win because these students get a part-time

280
00:13:57.184 --> 00:14:01.044
job learning on the job under experienced teachers while the

281
00:14:01.084 --> 00:14:03.924
people who... And there's a member here from Christchurch may have visited the

282
00:14:03.964 --> 00:14:07.844
school. She has, and it's a really, really exciting

