00:14:07.884 --> 00:14:11.814
thing for the students, but also who get more teachers and

284
00:14:11.844 --> 00:14:15.644
more adults in their classroom, but also for these student teachers who

285
00:14:15.704 --> 00:14:19.534
get more on-the-job training. Because I can tell you, everyone I've

286
00:14:19.564 --> 00:14:23.404
talked to says taking on 30 kids for six hours a day is

287
00:14:23.464 --> 00:14:24.524
not for the faint-hearted.

288
00:14:24.664 --> 00:14:24.844
Mm.

289
00:14:24.984 --> 00:14:28.704
And if all you have in training is a bunch of Marxist claptrap that you got from

290
00:14:28.744 --> 00:14:31.244
your university, then they will eat you alive.

291
00:14:31.584 --> 00:14:33.884
And so this kind of on-the-job training is very helpful.

292
00:14:34.204 --> 00:14:36.344
Okay. Supplementary question from Carl Bates.

