00:19:54.576 --> 00:19:58.496
And there's one other school, I forget which, but which is actually trying to rent

394
00:19:58.536 --> 00:19:59.356
more space. So,

395
00:20:00.296 --> 00:20:02.716
they're literally bursting at the seams.

396
00:20:03.016 --> 00:20:03.476
That's great.

397
00:20:03.656 --> 00:20:03.856
Great.

398
00:20:03.936 --> 00:20:04.046
Thank you.

